src:
Debuterte i Eliteserien etter 1004 dager: – Jeg vil ikke sitte på benken enda en sesong, det er sikkert
04 Nov 2019, 06:05 by Vegard Bjelland
Even Barli pådro seg hjernerystelse mot Viking onsdag. Da fikk endelig Magnus Lenes debuten sin.

RANHEIM - STABÆK 0–2
text:
Debuted in the Elite Series after 1004 days: - I don't want to sit on the bench for another season, that's for sure
04 Nov 2019, 06:05 by Vegard Bjelland
Even Barli suffered a concussion against Viking on Wednesday. Then Magnus Lenes finally made his debut.

RANHEIM - STABÆK 0–2
